      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t可能知道，也可能不知道，毕竟现在内参都要受到审查，谁知道这些审查官员给习近平看的啥玩意了。<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly9tLmR3LmNvbS96aC8lRTQlQjklQTAlRTYlQjAlOEYlRTQlQjglODAlRTglQTglODAlRTUlQTAlODItJUU1JTg2JTg1JUU1JThGJTgyJUU0JUI4JThEJUU1JTg2JThEJUU3JUIyJUJFJUU1JUJEJUE5L2EtNjM2MDY2OTQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://m.dw.com/zh/%E4%B9%A0%E6%B0%8F%E4%B8%80%E8%A8%80%E5%A0%82-%E5%86%85%E5%8F%82%E4%B8%8D%E5%86%8D%E7%B2%BE%E5%BD%A9/a-63606694\">https://m.dw.com/zh/%E4%B9%A0%E6%B0%8F%E4%B8%80%E8%A8%80%E5%A0%82-%E5%86%85%E5%8F%82%E4%B8%8D%E5%86%8D%E7%B2%BE%E5%BD%A9/a-63606694</a> </div>",
      "date": "2023-06-28",
      "agree_count": 5,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "665951",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "雙加不好的鴨語者",
        "uid": "22079"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t最近成績太差，差不多到大考了，要怎樣辦？<br/>\n明天再努力！(當什麼事都沒有看到)\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2023-06-28",
      "agree_count": 3,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "667252",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "客观评价习近平",
        "uid": "84033"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t经济烂下去，对于独裁者来说不是坏事<br/>\n毛时代制造物质稀缺，而政府又掌握分配物资的权力，这样才能让人们驯服\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2023-07-03",
      "agree_count": 3,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "667946",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "dignity",
        "uid": "50466"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t还“长期”呢！没有什么长期，现在就在崩溃的过程中。但是他不在乎，军警宪特在手就觉得一切都稳如泰山了。<br/>\n<br/>\n本质上是一种幻觉。\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2023-07-05",
      "agree_count": 2,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "666079",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "c2h4",
        "uid": "101813"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t肯定知道，知道也没用，几座大山压着，如果我是他我吃饱了吊死在办公室多好，哈哈这烂摊子给你们玩吧我先去了，人间不值得啊！\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2023-06-28",
      "agree_count": 2,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "666183",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "长歌当哭",
        "uid": "85967"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t包子说了<br/>\n<br/>\n要算总账<br/>\n<br/>\n要算政治帐<br/>\n<br/>\n所以经济不行没关系<br/>\n<br/>\n只要包子还在台上他一算<br/>\n<br/>\nokk了\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2023-06-29",
      "agree_count": 2,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "667084",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "總加速濕",
        "uid": "73156"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t先问是不是，再问为什么。<br/>\n首先，他知道什么是经济吗？\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2023-07-03",
      "agree_count": 1,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "667078",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "emiyafate",
        "uid": "112967"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t他应该知道很大一部分。但问题是作为独裁者他没有动力去解决这些问题。他的大部分精力应该是放在享乐和巩固自己权力上，而不是解决老百姓面临的主要问题上。\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2023-07-03",
      "agree_count": 2,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "665931",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "elsaanna",
        "uid": "24409"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t好又如何，早晚是要和美国脱钩的，你不能用常人的思维去思考独裁者\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2023-06-28",
      "agree_count": 1,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "665947",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "之江新军",
        "uid": "92363"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t习近平同志为高质量发展指明了方向。中国式现代化伟大斗争从胜利走向胜利。形势不是小好，是大好。恐美、媚美、跪美没有市场了！\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2023-06-28",
      "agree_count": 1,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "665948",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "kxy",
        "uid": "99835"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t笑，包帝就是知道无论怎么做，中国的经济都会越来越差，所以才敢这么玩啊。\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2023-06-28",
      "agree_count": 1,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "667269",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "本质理解",
        "uid": "92133"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t理中客都不一定认为中国经济会越来越差。<br/>\n习主席他老人家也许比理中客们更看好中国经济呢\t\t</div>",
